OL,3,CThe seaside town hit by infected
OL,4,Cdrinking water and misinformation
OL,6,FWatch Sam Blackledge's report on the
OL,7,Fone year anniversary of Brixham's
OL,8,Finfected water crisis
OL,10,FThe town of Brixham in South Devon is
OL,11,Fpeaceful, picturesque and welcoming.
OL,12,FBut for six sun-drenched weeks in the
OL,13,Fsummer of 2024, there was only one
OL,14,Fsubject on everybody's minds - water.
OL,16,FWhen the news broke on 13 May about a
OL,17,Fpotential public health scare, it
OL,18,Fwasn't initially clear what exactly
OL,19,Fthe town was dealing with.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
