OL,3,CThe seaside town hit by infected
OL,4,Cdrinking water and misinformation
OL,6,FSome people even reported becoming ill
OL,7,Fwith kidney stones due to avoiding
OL,8,Fwater altogether.
OL,10,FMy main memory of that period is of
OL,11,Fendlessly knocking on doors in the
OL,12,FHillhead area of the town - close to
OL,13,Fthe reservoir at the centre of the
OL,14,Fcontamination - and chatting to
OL,15,Fresidents about the most intimate
OL,16,Fdetails of their family's health.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
