OL,3,CThe seaside town hit by infected
OL,4,Cdrinking water and misinformation
OL,6,FVomiting, diarrhoea, stomach pains and
OL,7,Fstool samples are not usually subjects
OL,8,Fwe are terribly comfortable
OL,9,Fdiscussing. But it felt essential for
OL,10,Fpeople to share their stories and
OL,11,Fpiece together what on earth was going
OL,12,Fon.
OL,14,FCalls for resignation
OL,16,FOf the dozens of people we interviewed
OL,17,Flast summer, a handful stick in my
OL,18,Fmind.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
