OL,3,CThe seaside town hit by infected
OL,4,Cdrinking water and misinformation
OL,6,FIn mid-June I visited Karen Taylor who
OL,7,Fwas caring for her terminally ill 93-
OL,8,Fyear-old mother, Audrey.
OL,10,FKaren told me several of her
OL,11,Fneighbours had been hospitalised and
OL,12,Fshe feared for her mum's health if she
OL,13,Fwere to become ill.
OL,15,F"She wouldn't stand a chance," Karen
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,FI was also struck by a pair of
OL,19,Ftenacious next-door neighbours in
OL,20,FHillhead, Tanya Matthews and Michaela
OL,21,FLewis.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
