OL,3,CThe seaside town hit by infected
OL,4,Cdrinking water and misinformation
OL,6,FMichaela was one of the first to
OL,7,Fpublicly call for the chief executive,
OL,8,FSusan Davey, to resign over her
OL,9,Fhandling of the crisis.
OL,11,F'We still get people asking if the
OL,12,Fwater is alright'
OL,14,FToday, exactly one year on from the
OL,15,Foutbreak, the town is looking as
OL,16,Fglorious as ever. But the effects of
OL,17,Flast summer are still being felt.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
