OL,3,CThe seaside town hit by infected
OL,4,Cdrinking water and misinformation
OL,6,FHerve Regent runs the Beacon House bed
OL,7,Fand breakfast. Speaking to me on his
OL,8,Fpenthouse balcony, high up above the
OL,9,Ftown's famous harbour, he makes it
OL,10,Fclear he is not a fan of reporters.
OL,12,F"It's been difficult," he said. "The
OL,13,Fmain problem is trying to put Brixham
OL,14,Fback on the map.
OL,16,F"There were some irresponsible
OL,17,Fjournalists. We had 3,000 negative
OL,18,Fcomments on social media, in the
OL,19,Fnewspaper, on TV and radio, but not
OL,20,Fjust in the UK, internationally as
OL,21,Fwell.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
