OL,3,CThe seaside town hit by infected
OL,4,Cdrinking water and misinformation
OL,6,F"For example, I had someone from
OL,7,FGermany call me last year to cancel a
OL,8,Froom. They said 'We're cancelling
OL,9,Fbecause we heard we cannot take a
OL,10,Fshower in your B&B.'
OL,12,F"That's quite upsetting, especially
OL,13,Fknowing that the actual contaminated
OL,14,Fwater was coming from Hillhead
OL,15,FReservoir, while we are supplied by
OL,16,Fthe Aston reservoir, which is not
OL,17,Fcontaminated at all."
OL,19,FJoe Lowe, who runs the Brookside Guest
OL,20,FHouse, says the town is gradually
OL,21,Fgetting back to normal.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
