OL,3,CThe seaside town hit by infected
OL,4,Cdrinking water and misinformation
OL,6,F"It's not back to where it was before,
OL,7,Fbut we are seeing a recovery.
OL,9,F"We're still getting guests coming
OL,10,Fthis year who say 'Is the water
OL,11,Falright?' We've probably got the best
OL,12,Fwater in the South West at the moment
OL,13,Fbecause of everything they've done."
OL,15,F'I still don't trust the tap water'
OL,17,FDespite assurances from South West
OL,18,FWater that everything is fine,
OL,19,Fresidents are still divided on whether
OL,20,For not they trust the water coming out
OL,21,Fof their taps.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
