OL,6,FCohort study
OL,8,FThere were, in total, 126 confirmed
OL,9,Fcases of Cryptosporidiosis in Brixham
OL,10,Flast year.
OL,12,FBut the UK Health Security Agency is
OL,13,Fcarrying out a cohort study to
OL,14,Fdetermine the true number of cases,
OL,15,Fwhich could be considerably higher.
OL,17,FThe results will be published once the
OL,18,FDrinking Water Inspectorate has
OL,19,Fcompleted its own investigation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
