OL,3,CThe seaside town hit by infected
OL,4,Cdrinking water and misinformation
OL,6,FA South West Water spokesman told ITV
OL,7,FNews West Country: "We are sorry for
OL,8,Fwhat happened in Brixham last year `
OL,9,Fwhile we can't undo what happened, we
OL,10,Fhave made already made improvements to
OL,11,Fmake sure it cannot happen here again.
OL,13,F"Our focus is firmly on the future for
OL,14,Fcustomers and communities and we are
OL,15,Fworking to support local tourism in
OL,16,Fthe area.
OL,18,F"We are prioritising long-term
OL,19,Fimprovements so that every community
OL,20,Fwe serve can continue to rely on us."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
